1. Adjust Permissions

`sudo chmod -R a+r /opt/nso47`


2. load-path change in /opt/nso47/etc/ncs/ncs.conf (copy from /opt/nso45)

```
<load-path>
  <dir>./packages</dir>
  <dir>${NCS_DIR}/etc/ncs</dir>
  <dir>${NCS_DIR}/etc/ncs/snmp</dir>
</load-path>
```

```
<load-path>
   <dir>./packages</dir>
   <dir>/opt/nso/packages/neds/</dir>
   <dir>${NCS_DIR}/etc/ncs</dir>
   <dir>${NCS_DIR}/etc/ncs/snmp</dir>
 </load-path>
```
